\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\sb60\sa60\sl288\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}33.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}In considering Ms Wong's submissions,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}it is,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}I think,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}important to bear in mind that we are looking at the situation with the benefit of hindsight.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Hindsight may show that some additional precaution was necessary but this fact by itself would not prove that the defendant was guilty of negligence at the relevant date of the accident.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}As Cons JA put it in the}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Wayfoong}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}case at page}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}263H:}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} " }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Most risks can be reduced,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}or perhaps eliminated,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}by more stringent precautions,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}but the law of negligence is based,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}not on the absolute,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}but on what can reasonably be expected}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}"}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
