\pard\plain\ltrpar\qj\ri400\sb60\sa60\sl288\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch ,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}in the context of a claim by an employee against his employer,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Lord Reid said:}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} "}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}It is the duty of an employer,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}in considering whether some precaution should be taken against a foreseeable risk,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}to weigh,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}on the one hand,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the magnitude of the risk,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the likelihood of an accident happening and the possible seriousness of the consequences if an accident does happen,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}and,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}on the other hand,}{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the difficulty and expense and any other disadvantage of taking the precaution}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}" (}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Emphasis added}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0})}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
