{\listtext\pard\qj\fi14\ri400\sb60\sa60 0	}\pard\plain{\ltrpar\qj\fi14\ri400\sb60\sa60{\*\abilist\abilistid1021\abilistparentid0\abilistlevel1\abistartat0{\abifieldfont NULL}{\abilistdecimal .}{\abilistdelim %L}{\abiliststyle Numbered List}}{\*\pn\pnql\pnstart0\pnlvlbody\pndec{\pntxtb }{\pntxta }}\fn14\ls11\ilvl0\sl288\slmult1\itap0{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch [48}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}] "}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Cases of fire damage are likely to be very difficult to bring within the rule because}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} (}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}1}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}) }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}it is the}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} '}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}thing}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}' }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}which had been brought onto}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the land which must escape,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}not the fire which was started or increased by the}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} '}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}thing}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}'}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} (}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}2}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}) }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}While fire may be a dangerous thing,}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the occasions when fire as such is brought onto the land may be limited to cases where the fire has been deliberately or negligently started by the occupier or one for whom he is responsible.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0} }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Is this not a relic of the ignis suus rule}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}? (}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}3}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}) }{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}In any event starting a fire on one's land may well be an ordinary use of the land}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}"}{\f0\fs20\lang1033{\*\listtag0}.}{\f0\fs20\lang1033\ltrch\abiltr{\*\listtag0}\par}
